sect2.para:
A potential deadlock in the &man.usb.4;
	stack triggered by detaching USB devices that create character
	devices has been fixed.

sect4.para:
Support for Ralink RT5370 and
	    RT5372 chipsets has been added to the &man.run.4;
	    driver.

Support for the ASUS USB-N10 Nano
	    wireless card has been added to the &man.urtwn.4;
	    driver.

A bug in the fast receiver buffer
	    recycle path has been fixed in the &man.cxgbe.4;
	    driver.

sect3.para:
The &man.geom.8;
	  GEOM_MULTIPATH class has been updated to
	  support automatic live partition resizing.

Support for
	  BIO_DELETE has been added to &man.zfs.8;
	  zvol volumes.

Fixed accounting of
	  BIO_FLUSH operation in &man.geom.8;
	  GEOM_DISK class

sect2.para:
Support for the account
	facility has been added to the &man.pam.group.8;
	module.
